The recommended NodeJS module is:

  https://github.com/fmarier/node-libravatar


Testing
--------

Clone the module under ~/devel/remote/node-libravatar:

  cd ~/devel/remote/
  git clone git://github.com/fmarier/node-libravatar.git

and symlink it into place:

  ln -s ~/devel/remote/node-libravatar/lib/libravatar.js node_modules/libravatar/index.js

Then run the service:

  node libravatar-test.js

and visit the site at:

  http://localhost:3000/
